===message:I totally agree with the fact that the British were greedy.  Colonists should have not been expected to participate in any taxation to benefit the King and/or Parliament's war debt.  On the other hand, I don't think both the Colonists and British were unwilling to compromise.  I got the impression that the Colonists were willing to give a little, just not a lot, to the Parliament who was not giving them proper representation.
