===message:The one thing I believe your post is missing is the fact that the British were not only trying to secure repayment of debt from the Americans, they were also trying to raise revenue to pay their own royals and officers, who were clearly not selected by the colonists.  The colonists did not have much to say about who Parliment had in their cabinet and yet they had to pay extra taxes to provide revenue for these people?  It hardly seems fair.
